  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户登录查询的流程图。场景是：客户端输入用户名，然后通过DAO层去服务端查询用户信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cliente - Input username",
        "Cliente - DAO getUserByUsername"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是客户端的用户名输入框，然后调用本地的DAO方法。这个DAO是直连数据库，还是要走网络请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cliente - Input username",
        "Cliente - DAO getUserByUsername"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "要走HTTP请求到服务端。DAO层封装了HTTP调用，发送到Servidor的Webservice。中间需要明确标出是HTTP请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cliente - DAO getUserByUsername",
        "Servidor - Webservice",
        "Petició HTTP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了从客户端DAO到服务端Webservice的箭头，标注为Petició HTTP。接下来服务端内部怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cliente - DAO getUserByUsername",
        "Servidor - Webservice"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Webservice收到请求后，要先做数据校验，然后调用服务端的DAO去查询用户表。这里需要两个节点：校验和DAO查询。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Servidor - Webservice",
        "Servidor - DAO Usuarios",
        "Valida datos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
